.keep-reading.ch-container
	.ch-g1-2
		.ch-leftcolumn
			h2 Keep reading
			- if (label)
				p
					| Find more in 
					a(href="/api/#{version}/symbols/ch.#{label}.html") #{label} API documentation
					| . There you'll find the most complete info of this component and others.
			- else
				p
					| Read more on our 
					a(href="/api") API documentation
					| . There you'll find the most complete info of all components.
	.ch-g1-2
		.ch-rightcolumn
			h2 Troubleshooting
			p
				| You can easily report issues through our 
				- if (label)
					a(href="https://github.com/mercadolibre/chico/issues/new?title=#{label}:%20", target="_blank") issue tracker
				- else
					a(href="https://github.com/mercadolibre/chico/issues/new", target="_blank") issue tracker
				| , or simply tweet to 
				a(href="http://twitter.com/chicoui", target="_blank") @chicoui
				| .